Information About the Post
<!--No longer passing the render method a string - passing it key value pairs-->
<!--First key value pair tells Rails the name of the partial to render-->
<!--The second key value pair specifies the locals as a Hash. That Hash's keys(post_author) will be a local variable within the partial-->
<%= render partial: 'authors/author', locals: {post_author: @post.author}%>
<%= @post.title %>
<%= @post.content %>
